<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1353477-would-you-recommend-reading-the-hot-zone">Would you recommend reading The Hot Zone before The Demon in the Freezer?

I understand that as nonfiction, reading order shouldn&#39;t matter, but since the subject matter of the two books is similar, I just wondered if I would be in the dark on anything by going into Demon first.</a>
</div>
