<div id="review_3235860934" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3235860934" />
    <a title="Jaimie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2949290-jaimie"><img alt="Jaimie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1582898622p2/2949290.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3235860934?book_show_action=true">Mar 26, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jaimie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jaimie" href="/user/show/2949290-jaimie">Jaimie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780755312184" href="/book/show/198505.The_Demon_in_the_Freezer">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3235860934" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3007416527442532284">I am giving this 5-stars. It was very well written and informative. An eye opener for sure, especially with the COVID-19 pandemic in our current world. The last few pages were poignant when predicting the spread of future viruses, health care in third world countries (and even our own apparently) and population surges—how quickly the spread can be and how dire it may become if not curtailed. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


